description:
In this video, we're going to learn how to sing "When the Roll Is Called Up Yonder" (Karaoke key: F). This classic hymn is a great way to worship with your friends or family, and it's surprisingly easy to learn.

If you're looking for a fun way to spend a Sunday evening, give this hymn a try! It only takes a few minutes to learn, and you and your friends or family are sure to have a great time singing it together. Thanks for watching!
(Gaither Homecoming Style)
